% nico, carbide

# Copy Certificates
```
kubectl -n nico-system get secret nico-admin-cli-client -o jsonpath='{.data.client\.crt}' | base64 -d > tmp/clis/config/client.crt
kubectl -n nico-system get secret nico-admin-cli-client -o jsonpath='{.data.client\.key}' | base64 -d > tmp/clis/config/client.key
kubectl -n nico-system get secret nico-admin-cli-client -o jsonpath='{.data.ca\.crt}' | base64 -d > tmp/clis/config/ca.crt
```
